Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.23,0:01:37.98,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej, senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.98,0:01:40.48,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Môžem na tebe vyskúšať svoj nový chmat?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.48,0:01:42.61,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nazvala som ho "Stvrdená za 120 hodín"!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.61,0:01:45.95,Dialogue-TK,,0,0,0,,One, two, here we go, let's dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.61,0:01:45.95,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One, two, ups, let's dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.95,0:01:47.95,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No tak, bude to fajn!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.95,0:01:50.66,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No tak.  Môj nový chmat!  Môj nový chmaaat!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.66,0:01:52.66,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je to proste "BAM"!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.87,0:01:55.79,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nie sú zlaté, Shiina-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.79,0:01:57.16,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aké nerozumné.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.16,0:01:58.83,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Počúvaš vôbec?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.83,0:01:59.71,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ako fakt?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.67,0:02:05.28,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vážne, to je toto základka?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.67,0:02:06.04,Dialogue-Alt,,0,0,0,,No dobre no!  Pôjdem sa spýtať Ooyamy-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.72,0:02:07.30,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prichádzajú len idioti.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.43,0:02:11.35,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej. To si hovoril o {\i1}mne{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.35,0:02:12.56,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ja som Boh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.81,0:02:15.92,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ha?  To si s tým ešte furt neprestal?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.92,0:02:18.69,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Po tom, čo si plakal v Otonashiho rukách?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.69,0:02:20.06,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ktože to plakal?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.15,0:02:23.18,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To ty tu budeš plakať.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.18,0:02:26.03,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tak, uvedom si podstatu štipcov na bielizeň.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.44,0:02:29.45,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uvedom si, aký si oproti štipcom na bielizeň bezvýznamný...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.45,0:02:30.78,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a zúfaj.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.54,0:02:37.08,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Š-Štipce na bielizeň...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.08,0:02:38.41,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Môžu držať veci...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.41,0:02:39.92,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Môžu ich držať a nespadnú!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.92,0:02:41.51,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tvoje šaty sa nezašpinia!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.51,0:02:42.79,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Úžasné!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.79,0:02:46.42,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ahh!  Môžu byť dokonca náhradou za spinky!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.42,0:02:49.26,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,V porovnaní s tým, čo som {\i1}ja{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.26,0:02:51.14,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nie som dobrý vôbec k ničomu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.93,0:02:51.14,Dialogue-Alt,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.14,0:02:53.58,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nepoužívaj hypnózu na pomstu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.58,0:02:55.81,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Otonashi-san!  Dobré ráno!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.81,0:02:57.26,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo to má byť?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.26,0:02:59.46,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To on si začal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.46,0:03:01.52,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ja sa snažím byť najpokojnejší, ako sa dá.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.52,0:03:02.94,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo je na tomto pokojné?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.36,0:03:06.57,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Muž kľačí a ide si vyplakať oči.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.03,0:03:08.69,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Otonashi-kun, Naoi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.15,0:03:10.30,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Niečo s vami chcem prebrať.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.30,0:03:11.57,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Poďte sem, prosím.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.52,0:03:14.53,AB Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1389.333,262.333)}Nažive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:16.33,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo sa deje?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.79,0:03:18.20,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Volať nás na takéto miesto...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.48,0:03:22.46,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naoi-kun, chcem, aby \Nsi skúsil Otonashimu-kun obnoviť spomienky.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:24.71,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prikazuješ mi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.71,0:03:26.71,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kto si myslíš, že si?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.71,0:03:28.26,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tvoja vodkyňa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.26,0:03:29.51,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tvoja nadriadená.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.51,0:03:31.42,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Proste rob, čo ti povie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.42,0:03:31.72,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Počkať...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.09,0:03:33.51,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moje spomienky?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.51,0:03:35.68,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Správne.  Tvoje spomienky.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.68,0:03:37.85,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hypnóza Naoiho-kun je fakt niečo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.27,0:03:41.10,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mal by byť schopný vrátiť ti stratené spomienky.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.10,0:03:42.98,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm, chápem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.98,0:03:45.22,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Určite by som to chcel skúsiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:46.57,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.57,0:03:48.23,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nerozhodujete o tom sami.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.23,0:03:49.49,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aký je problém?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.49,0:03:51.49,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To nám chceš tvrdiť, že si nechceš spomenúť?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.49,0:03:53.11,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah... no, ja len...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.12,0:03:56.03,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Chcem si na to spomenúť...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.03,0:03:58.24,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ale... čo ten pocit úzkosti?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.74,0:04:02.71,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Je to... preto, že kvôli spomienkam...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.71,0:04:05.21,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}možno takýto život skončí?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.59,0:04:07.38,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Počkať, ja...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.25,0:04:09.55,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To sa mi naozaj...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.17,0:04:12.17,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}až tak zapáčilo byť s týmito ľuďmi?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.93,0:04:15.59,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No ak si spomeniem na svoju minulosť...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.59,0:04:19.43,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}budem ešte stále môcť pokračovať ako doteraz?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.97,0:04:21.47,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ale... aj tak{\fscx300}-{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.47,0:04:22.18,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,50)}Otonashi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.31,0:04:26.69,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No dobre.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.06,0:04:28.94,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je jedno, akú máš miulosť...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.94,0:04:30.57,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,prosím, nestrať o sebe mienku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.27,0:04:32.90,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je jedno, čo sa ti stane...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.28,0:04:35.57,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vždy budem na tvojej strane.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.45,0:04:38.83,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prosím, povedz niečo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.83,0:04:41.50,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tiež som na tvojej strane.  Nemáš sa čoho báť.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.50,0:04:43.00,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vďaka, pomohlo mi počuť to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.00,0:04:44.83,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo?  Aký v tom bol rozdiel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.17,0:04:47.38,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No dobre.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.79,0:04:49.34,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prosím, sadni si.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.92,0:04:53.92,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tak teda začnime.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.06,0:05:06.15,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Braček, baví ťa škola?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.15,0:05:07.77,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To ani trochu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.77,0:05:08.44,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ani tam nechodím.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:11.32,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keby si tam chodil, možno by ťa bavila.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.32,0:05:14.11,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keby som bol trochu múdrejší, tak možno hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.11,0:05:15.78,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Som dosť blbý...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.78,0:05:19.07,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nie je to miesto pre ľudí, čo nevedia udržať dobré známky.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.07,0:05:20.79,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nie je učenie zábava?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.79,0:05:22.33,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jasné že nie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.33,0:05:23.45,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je to učenie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.45,0:05:26.79,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A čo kamaráti?  Hrávaš sa s kamarátmi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.79,0:05:30.04,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kukať telku alebo hrať hry sám je oveľa väčšia sranda.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.50,0:05:33.26,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hrať sa s ostatnými a nasledovať ich...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.26,0:05:36.68,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,smiať sa na ich vtipoch, aj keď nie sú vtipné...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.68,0:05:37.97,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,len ma to unavuje.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.97,0:05:41.31,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fakt?  Ja sa na učenie teším.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.31,0:05:43.22,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Teším sa aj na kamarátov!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.89,0:05:46.23,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej, pravda...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.48,0:05:49.31,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tu máš.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.94,0:05:54.86,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ďakujem, braček!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.44,0:05:56.99,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ty debil!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.91,0:06:03.08,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ja... neviem, prečo som nažive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.08,0:06:04.29,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nemám žiadny dôvod žiť.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.87,0:06:06.58,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nemám záujem o druhých.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.12,0:06:09.29,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Žiť bez starosti o druhých...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.29,0:06:11.00,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tak sa žije ľahšie.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.79,0:06:15.30,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pracoval som len preto, aby som si zarobil na jedlo...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.63,0:06:18.13,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Taký život mi úplne stačil...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.59,0:06:21.64,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ale aj tak som stále...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.64,0:06:23.76,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stále som navštevoval svoju mladšiu sestru.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.81,0:06:26.18,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}S mojimi skromnými príjmami...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.18,0:06:27.81,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Som jej kupoval mangu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.81,0:06:30.56,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Vždy som proste išiel do kníhkupectva...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.56,0:06:33.32,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a náhodne zobral niečo z výkladu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.32,0:06:35.32,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Takže som ani nevedel, či je to ten istý časopis.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.90,0:06:38.82,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Je možné, že to bol iný časopis...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.82,0:06:40.99,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a nemohla čítať príbehy v poradí.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.57,0:06:42.07,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ale...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.07,0:06:43.83,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ďakujem, braček!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.20,0:06:47.16,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sestra vždy povedala len toto.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.16,0:06:50.04,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Vyzerala, že by bola šťastná za čokoľvek.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.83,0:06:52.59,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Moja sestra bola iná ako ja...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.09,0:06:55.42,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mala nádej vo svoj život.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.42,0:06:58.34,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Určite by bola schopná si nájsť dôvod žiť.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.34,0:06:59.63,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A napriek tomu...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.63,0:07:01.43,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}už dva roky...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.43,0:07:03.39,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}celú tú dobu žila len na nemocničnej posteli.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.97,0:07:05.43,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bolo mi jej ľúto...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.43,0:07:07.06,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rád by som sa s ňou vymenil.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.68,0:07:09.64,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Keby sa mohla vymeniť so mnou...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.64,0:07:11.85,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}bez štipky nádeje, bez dôvodu žiť...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.90,0:07:14.61,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tento súcit...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.61,0:07:16.44,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}má nútil vracať sa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.32,0:07:19.70,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Prišla zima.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.24,0:07:21.95,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Leto bolo dosť zlé...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.95,0:07:24.12,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ale moja práca bola v zime ešte horšia.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.12,0:07:25.78,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Necítil som si končeky prstov...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.78,0:07:27.08,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}cítil som sa, akoby mi mali odpadnúť.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.12,0:07:29.12,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ale aj tak...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.12,0:07:30.37,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}som ďalej žil.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.62,0:07:32.12,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Žil...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.21,0:07:34.34,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kvôli čomu?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.29,0:07:36.80,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nemal by som o tom premýšľať...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.80,0:07:40.17,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ak o tom budem premýšľať, asi by som proste skončil.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.17,0:07:42.13,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Musím aspoň robiť toto...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.13,0:07:43.07,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aby som mohol jesť...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.07,0:07:46.51,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a kupovať darčeky pre moju mladšiu sestru.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.77,0:07:51.94,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Presne tak.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.94,0:07:54.40,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Na Vianoce sa porozprávam s doktorom...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.40,0:07:57.02,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a postarám sa, aby mohla ísť aspoň na chvíľu von.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.65,0:08:00.69,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rozmýšľam, či sa dá chodiť vozíkom aj po snehu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.24,0:08:03.20,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No... Ak nie, proste ju budem niesť.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.20,0:08:06.24,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mal by som ju zvládnuť odniesť bez problémov.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.24,0:08:09.66,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Potom pôjdeme do jej obľúbeného obchodu a kúpim jej, čo len bude chcieť.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.66,0:08:13.71,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Najradšej by som ju zobral do nejakej dobrej cukrárne na koláč.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.71,0:08:16.04,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mal by som začať šetriť.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.09,0:08:21.67,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ak by si mohla ísť na Vianoce von, kam by si šla?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.67,0:08:23.30,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Na hlavnú ulicu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.30,0:08:24.97,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naozaj?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.97,0:08:28.35,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Všetky stromy tam na sebe majú svetielka!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.35,0:08:29.39,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vedel si to?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.39,0:08:32.18,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nie... Na Vianoce tam moc nechodím...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.18,0:08:34.77,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Počula som, že je to krásne!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.77,0:08:36.81,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Minulý rok to vraj bolo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.81,0:08:38.44,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Povedal mi to doktor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.91,0:08:41.32,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tak tam pôjdeme?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.99,0:08:43.24,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Môžem?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.24,0:08:45.11,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Skúsim vybaviť, aby si mohla.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.11,0:08:47.87,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A ak povedia nie... Vezmem ťa von tajne.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.87,0:08:48.58,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naozaj?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.58,0:08:49.99,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej, naozaj.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.99,0:08:52.71,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Super!  Ďakujem, braček!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.62,0:08:57.00,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To bolo najväčšie ďakujem, aké som kedy dostal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.34,0:09:01.21,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo to robíš?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.21,0:09:02.34,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prepáčte!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.84,0:09:05.05,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Začal som pracovať na viacerých miestach.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.68,0:09:08.10,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Doma som už len spal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.76,0:09:11.64,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Teraz, keď mám cieľ, cítim, že dokážem pracovať.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.73,0:09:14.31,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Moja jediná starosť bola...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.06,0:09:18.81,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}že jej stav sa zhoršoval.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.32,0:09:22.82,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Povolenie na vychádzku som, samozrejme, nedostal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:25.20,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Takže som...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.20,0:09:26.82,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}čakal, kým sa skončia návštevné hodiny...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.82,0:09:28.78,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}vkradol som sa do jej izby...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.78,0:09:31.37,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a vzal ju do nočného mesta.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.83,0:09:38.21,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Váu!  Hej, vidíš to?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.21,0:09:39.33,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je to úžasné.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.33,0:09:42.71,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej.  Je to krásne.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.71,0:09:43.71,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Že?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.71,0:09:45.66,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je to tak krásne.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.66,0:09:47.51,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Som rád, že to tiež vidím.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.51,0:09:48.59,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A to len vďaka tebe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.55,0:09:53.31,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A teraz bude zábava pokračovať!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.31,0:09:55.27,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ako prvé - darček!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.27,0:09:56.85,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kúpim ti hocičo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.85,0:10:01.11,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tvoj braček pre tento deň našetril spústu peňazí.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.11,0:10:03.69,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takže ti kúpim všetko, kľudne aj niečo drahé.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.69,0:10:04.94,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo by si chcela?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.94,0:10:06.65,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Najskôr poďme do obchodu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.65,0:10:08.61,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Môže byť aj klenotníctvo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.61,0:10:10.53,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alebo by ti stačil normálny obchodný dom?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.53,0:10:11.62,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Braček...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.87,0:10:13.08,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.08,0:10:14.75,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ďakujem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.29,0:10:18.58,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dobre!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.31,0:10:22.88,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Po nakupovaní na teba čaká ešte spústa dobrých vecí!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.88,0:10:24.46,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ďalej je večera!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.46,0:10:29.05,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O týchto veciach moc neviem, ale rezervoval som pekné miesto z časopisu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.05,0:10:31.39,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Servírujú tam v chodoch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.39,0:10:34.01,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Večera so všetkými chodmi!  Skvelé, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.01,0:10:35.18,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tiež to skúsim prvýkrát.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.77,0:10:41.15,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1100)}{\i1}Potom som pokračoval v monológu a ďalej kráčal...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.52,0:10:44.23,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ja už pôjdem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.23,0:10:46.74,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naozaj tam môžeš žiť len tak sám?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.74,0:10:48.40,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nebudeš osamelý?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.40,0:10:49.57,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Budem v poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.57,0:10:50.57,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Som na to zvyknutý.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.57,0:10:53.70,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naozaj?  Naozaj budeš v poriadku?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.70,0:10:55.99,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ak ťa bude niečo trápiť, daj mi vedieť.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.99,0:10:59.00,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Môžeš sa k nám kedykoľvek prísť najesť.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.00,0:11:01.46,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Áno.  Veľmi pekne ďakujem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.83,0:11:04.84,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ďakujem za všetko, čo ste pre mňa urobili.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.38,0:11:08.38,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ja...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.92,0:11:11.09,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}som mal celý ten čas dôvod žiť...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.14,0:11:15.10,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ten dôvod bol... celý čas vedľa mňa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.27,0:11:17.98,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Len som si to neuvedomil.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.56,0:11:21.56,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Počuť ju povedať "Ďakujem"...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.56,0:11:23.73,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Len tým, že som to počul...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.73,0:11:25.19,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}som bol schopný žiť.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.98,0:11:27.86,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kvôli pocitu, že ma potrebuje...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.36,0:11:29.88,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}som sa cítil nažive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.95,0:11:32.61,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bol som šťastný.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.07,0:11:35.33,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Som taký hlupák,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.99,0:11:37.70,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}že som si to uvedomil až teraz.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.45,0:11:40.75,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bola pre mňa taká dôležitá...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.75,0:11:41.87,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a ja som pre ňu nič neurobil.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.04,0:11:44.63,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Celý čas bola...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.63,0:11:46.13,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}v nemocnici...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.46,0:11:48.88,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}{\i1}v ktorej mohla len čítať mangu, čo som jej kupoval.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.51,0:11:52.01,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Len s tým...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.01,0:11:53.51,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}S takým životom...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.60,0:11:56.81,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bola skutočne šťastná?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.72,0:11:59.06,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A potom...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.06,0:12:01.10,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Môj život potom, čo som ju stratil...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.48,0:12:03.31,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Skončil tiež?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.35,0:12:06.40,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dni, ktoré som trávil s neviditeľným šťastím...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.40,0:12:07.77,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tie časy odišli.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.78,0:12:11.15,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pre mňa...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.70,0:12:15.41,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tu už vôbec nič nezostalo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.41,0:12:20.79,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ďakujem za všetko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.79,0:12:22.79,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gratulujem k prepusteniu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.79,0:12:25.04,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ďakujem vám!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.42,0:12:26.79,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Postaraj sa o seba.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.01,0:12:36.30,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Možno znovu nájdem dôvod k životu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.80,0:12:39.56,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dôvod na život... Myslím, že ho dokážem nájsť.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.06,0:12:42.85,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ak môžem tento život...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.85,0:12:45.90,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}venovať niekomu inému...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.85,0:13:19.10,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Spomenul si si?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.64,0:13:20.60,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.60,0:13:24.18,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nevyzerá to, že povieš, že to bol skvelý život.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.18,0:13:26.56,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nachvíľu ma prosím nechajte samého.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.62,0:13:42.98,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mal som plytký a bezfarebný život.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.62,0:13:47.00,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kým si ma nenaučila, že je dôvod na život...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.27,0:13:48.75,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Našiel som ho...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.75,0:13:50.04,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A potom...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.04,0:13:51.88,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Som zomrel v polovici môjho sna?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.80,0:13:54.92,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Zomrel som bez toho, aby som niečo dokončil?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.72,0:13:57.49,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To nemôže byť pravda!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.80,0:13:58.89,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To nemôže...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.59,0:14:01.31,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nemôžem ani umrieť!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.06,0:14:03.27,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hatsune!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.15,0:14:15.53,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Upokojil si sa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.53,0:14:16.61,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.61,0:14:20.49,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je normálne cítiť sa smutne po návrate spomienok.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.49,0:14:21.99,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nie len u teba.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.66,0:14:27.25,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Som slabý, čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.87,0:14:30.42,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Myslím, že som si znova uvedomil, aká si silná.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.42,0:14:31.96,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To nie je pravda.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.57,0:14:36.13,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,V každom prípade, zmenilo sa niečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.13,0:14:37.13,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.13,0:14:40.26,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tvoje pocity... budeš pokračovať v boji na Bojisku?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.64,0:14:43.10,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Budem pokračovať.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.10,0:14:44.77,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nemôžem takto umrieť.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.00,0:14:46.06,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chápem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.06,0:14:48.69,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vyzerá to, že si našiel dôvod.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.69,0:14:49.77,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.77,0:14:51.77,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zase sa na teba spoľahnem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.57,0:15:04.12,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takže, aké to máte hlásenie?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.70,0:15:07.66,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Na večer nemáme dostatok stravných lístkov.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.66,0:15:09.62,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo budeme robiť? Mali by sme to skúsiť s Tornádom?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.62,0:15:10.92,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.92,0:15:14.13,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dnešná operácia je... Monštrózny prúd!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.51,0:15:18.03,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Konečne je to tu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.03,0:15:19.93,Dialogue-TK,,0,0,0,,A carnival of despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.93,0:15:21.93,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo je to za operáciu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.59,0:15:24.64,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takže nejaké monštrá existujú?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.64,0:15:25.81,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,V tomto svete?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.81,0:15:28.14,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Áno.  Kráľ rieky.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.14,0:15:29.60,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kráľ rieky?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.60,0:15:31.69,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kúsok odtiaľto je rieka, nie?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.97,0:15:34.06,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tam získame zásoby potravín.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.44,0:15:38.94,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,P-Počkať... to ideme proste a jednoducho chytať ryby?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.25,0:15:41.99,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej... prečo? Čo sa deje?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.99,0:15:43.32,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh... nič.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.82,0:15:46.58,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Zase som sa nechal uniesť menom a predstavil som si niečo absurdné.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.09,0:15:50.87,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kto asi vyhrá?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.87,0:15:52.17,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Strašne sa teším~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.17,0:15:53.08,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.21,0:15:58.05,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo to tu robíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.68,0:16:10.35,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Popri ostatnom som aj záhradníčka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.94,0:16:15.48,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ch-Chápem..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.48,0:16:16.61,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh... hej!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.14,0:16:18.65,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tiež by si mala ísť!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.32,0:16:21.74,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Všetci ideme k rieke chytať ryby!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.74,0:16:22.57,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rieka?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.03,0:16:25.82,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ísť tam je proti pravidlám.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:26.62,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je to nebezpečné.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.62,0:16:28.41,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je to v poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.41,0:16:30.75,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Už nie si prezidentka študentskej rady.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.75,0:16:31.75,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Na chvíľu sa uvoľni.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.71,0:16:34.25,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ale stále som študentka...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.26,0:16:47.72,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prečo si ju zobral so sebou?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.72,0:16:48.97,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aký je problém?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.97,0:16:49.97,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nechajme ju pridať sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.97,0:16:51.06,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je to nepriateľ!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.06,0:16:52.98,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nepriateľ Bojiska!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.98,0:16:54.13,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Si debil, čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.13,0:16:55.10,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aké nerozumné.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.35,0:16:58.05,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Počúvajte ma.  Už nám nič nespraví. Nie je nepriateľ!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.05,0:17:00.86,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Áno, ale stále je tak {\i1}trocha{\i0} prezidentkou študentskej rady!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.86,0:17:03.99,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zhodou náhod tu je aj terajší prezident.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.99,0:17:05.36,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Presne tak.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.36,0:17:07.07,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ale hlavne som Boh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.07,0:17:08.95,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nie si Boh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.95,0:17:10.37,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo urobíme, Yurippe?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.04,0:17:16.79,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Už nie je prezidentka študentskej rady. Môže ísť.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.25,0:17:19.96,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Si v poriadku?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.96,0:17:22.42,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asi sme získali neuveriteľného člena...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.34,0:17:25.93,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej vlastne... prečo nemáte žiadnu výbavu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.93,0:17:28.35,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Už sme kontaktovali Guildu, takže to bude fajn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.80,0:17:31.37,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Máme tu na to príslušného maniaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.37,0:17:32.35,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maniak?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.86,0:17:39.73,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kto je to?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.73,0:17:41.02,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Volá sa Saitou.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.02,0:17:42.36,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Má vedomosti o zbraniach...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.36,0:17:46.03,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,ale v Guilde je známy ako Fish Saitou.  Je to rybársky maniak.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.99,0:17:52.49,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Všetky zásoby na túto rybačku priniesol vo voze.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.49,0:17:54.29,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To všetko?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.29,0:17:55.83,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ako až miluje rybárčenie?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.83,0:17:57.33,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ďalší debil, čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.46,0:17:59.50,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dobre.  Začnime!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.64,0:18:11.22,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aký debil.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.85,0:18:22.08,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Možno by som bol v tomto svete tvoj spojenec.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.08,0:18:23.48,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nikto taký tu nikdy nebol.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.48,0:18:25.11,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A nechcela by si, aby bola?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.11,0:18:26.57,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nikto taký nie je.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.57,0:18:28.95,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,436)}Aj keby boli, proste by zmizli.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.02,0:18:31.37,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tachibana...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.78,0:18:33.16,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My nezmizneme.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.16,0:18:35.79,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takže je v poriadku, keď sa s nami spriatelíš.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.79,0:18:38.33,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No tak, poďme všetci spolu chytať ryby.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.21,0:18:47.80,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo mám robiť teraz?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.80,0:18:48.80,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To nie, to nie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.18,0:18:53.72,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Najprv si vyberieš návnadu a potom na ňu zahákneš nejaké jedlo alebo červíka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.47,0:18:58.23,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ty nemáš problém s chrobákmi, hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.23,0:18:59.23,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo ďalej?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.85,0:19:02.73,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zamier na rieku a švihni celou silou.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.15,0:19:11.36,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Takeyamaaaaaa~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.36,0:19:14.99,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Volaj ma Kristuuuuus!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.99,0:19:17.79,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ty máš vážne supermanskú silu, čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.79,0:19:20.17,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Overdrive je pasívny.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.17,0:19:21.21,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pasívny?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.21,0:19:22.63,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Možno...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.92,0:19:26.38,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Možno... by to s tebou mohlo byť možné.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.10,0:19:28.34,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo by mohlo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.34,0:19:30.51,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chytiť Kráľa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.30,0:19:34.72,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ako hovorí meno operácie, tá vec je monštrum.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.77,0:19:39.23,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Niečo ťahá.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.07,0:19:50.45,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-Monštrózny prúd!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.94,0:19:51.82,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Toto?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.24,0:19:55.24,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Obyčajne sa Monštrózny prúd objavuje ako znak Kráľovho hnevu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.24,0:19:57.70,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keď sa to stane, všetci utečieme.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.70,0:19:58.58,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.16,0:20:00.83,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To dievča by to mohlo zvládnuť!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.25,0:20:04.58,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To myslíš vážne?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.58,0:20:06.67,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aká veľká je tá vec?!  Udica sa zlomí!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.92,0:20:09.26,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nepodceňuj moje remeslo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.26,0:20:11.38,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bolo to vyrobené, aby vydržalo aj Kráľa rieky!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.38,0:20:13.93,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aj tak, toto je nemožné!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.36,0:20:16.43,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo sa deje? Idete po Kráľovi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.43,0:20:17.99,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To určite nezaberie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.99,0:20:18.72,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Matsushita piaty!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.33,0:20:21.85,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dám ti mäsový udon.  Poď a pomôž!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.85,0:20:22.73,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Máš to mať!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.73,0:20:25.98,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oho, Hinata-senpai.  Vyzeráš tak nechránene.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.98,0:20:28.57,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fajn!  Čo keby som ťa kopla do zadku tak silno, že by si sa sa preletel?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.57,0:20:31.99,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prestaň vymýšľať kraviny a pomôž nám!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.49,0:20:34.16,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Potrebujeme posily!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.16,0:20:35.24,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To je Otonashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.71,0:20:36.83,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aký slaboch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.79,0:20:43.67,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej, vy!  Ťahajte silnejšie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.79,0:20:51.01,Dialogue-Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Raz dva!  Raz dva!  Raz dva!  \NRaz dva!  Raz dva!  Raz dva!  
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.63,0:20:49.21,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Teraz!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.89,0:20:58.05,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vytiahla ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.05,0:20:59.38,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A nás tiež!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.38,0:21:00.86,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kto je tu monštrum?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.86,0:21:01.85,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Táto situácia...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.85,0:21:02.93,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vyzerá zle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.98,0:21:05.73,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ak spadneme, zožerie nás!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.73,0:21:06.98,Dialogue-TK,,0,0,0,,Crazy for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.98,0:21:08.11,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Boh nikdy nepadá.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.80,0:21:10.94,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aké nerozumné.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.36,0:21:13.99,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zožerie nás!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.13,0:21:15.11,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Musím ich zachrániť.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.00,0:21:29.97,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej... s týmto na chvíľu nebudeme musieť použiť Tornádo, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.97,0:21:31.59,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To to budeme jesť každý deň?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.59,0:21:34.05,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ale hlavne, ako to chceme uskladniť?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.55,0:21:37.32,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej, vyhodiť to by bolo plytvanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.32,0:21:38.14,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asi nemáme na výber.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.58,0:21:41.72,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Spravme z toho jedno veľké jedlo a rozdáme ho obyčajným študentom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.72,0:21:43.59,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, dobrý nápad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.59,0:21:44.81,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Urobme to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.90,0:21:52.41,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Toto je ako charitatívna práca.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.41,0:21:55.70,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Toto nie je Bojisko... chováme sa skôr ako charita.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.70,0:21:58.27,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, už ani nemáme s kým bojovať.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.27,0:22:00.28,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Neskončilo sa už Bojisko?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.57,0:22:02.87,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tak čo by sme potom boli?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.58,0:22:07.15,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Tím Ulievame sa, aby sme nezmizli"?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.15,0:22:08.29,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čože to?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.42,0:22:10.99,Dialogue-TK,,0,0,0,,Chop, chop, chop, chop.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.50,0:22:15.30,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nikdy som si nemyslel, že by sme robili niečo také.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.05,0:22:21.81,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej, Tachibana.  Môžem ťa volať krstným menom?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.81,0:22:23.01,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.01,0:22:24.56,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lebo teraz sme si bližší.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.56,0:22:25.31,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sme?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.60,0:22:27.17,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A nie sme?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.17,0:22:30.06,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Spoločná rybačka... spoločné varenie...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.06,0:22:32.69,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a okrem toho... keď som ho prvýkrát počul...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.43,0:22:35.44,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pomyslel som si, "Aké nádherné meno."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.88,0:22:37.05,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Páči sa mi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.05,0:22:38.45,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Páči sa mi tvoje meno.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.16,0:22:41.57,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kanade zanemná, "hrať pieseň", však?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.57,0:22:44.91,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ak to tak chceš hovoriť, nevadí mi to.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.33,0:22:48.12,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moje meno je Yuzuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.12,0:22:50.29,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Píše sa to ako "zviazať strunu".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.12,0:22:50.29,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx93\fscy93}Poznámka: To môže znamenať tetivu alebo strunu hud. nástroja
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.29,0:22:51.08,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Môžeš ma tak volať.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.84,0:22:55.00,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dobre, Kanade.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.00,0:22:56.51,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rád by som ťa o niečo požiadal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.51,0:22:57.34,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.63,0:23:00.87,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mohla by si prosím teraz s nami zostať?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.87,0:23:02.07,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.07,0:23:05.22,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Už nechcem s nikým bojovať.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.93,0:23:07.48,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chcem, aby si s nami ostala a zabávala sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.64,0:23:12.48,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A... pretože...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.48,0:23:15.11,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Som rád s tebou.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.37,0:23:16.23,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chápem.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.51,0:23:19.11,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ak je to chceš, urobím to.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.50,0:23:23.24,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To je sľub, hej?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.64,0:23:24.53,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.91,0:23:31.75,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mimochodom, kde je Yurippe?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.75,0:23:33.75,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keď to spomínaš, tiež som ju nevidel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.24,0:23:36.81,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asi nás z niekadiaľ sleduje.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.81,0:23:40.59,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nie je zrovna ten typ, čo sa účastní na takýchto charitách.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.59,0:23:42.14,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej, tiež pomôžte!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.97,0:23:46.01,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yurippe!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.43,0:23:50.39,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yurippe!  Kto ti to urobil?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.50,0:23:52.40,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anjel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.56,0:23:53.69,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anjel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.94,0:23:59.61,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Počkať chvíľu!  Kanade bola celú dobu so mnou!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.21,0:24:11.58,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anjel?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.51,0:25:49.97,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Matsushita piaty!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.26,0:25:50.46,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takže sme uväznení.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.97,0:25:50.85,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Modlím sa, aby sme sa znova stretli.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.85,0:25:51.72,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pasca.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.85,0:25:53.22,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nemôžem proste {\i1}rozptýliť{\i0} niekoho tak desivého!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.72,0:25:52.60,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo sa to tu deje?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.32,0:25:53.72,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nechajte ma povedať jednu možnosť.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.60,0:25:53.97,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je Kanade v poriadku?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.22,0:25:53.97,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hráč Anjel...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.97,0:25:55.77,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nechám vás chytiť dych a potom vás presvedčím. {So, this line never actually made it into the next episode} {My mind is blown here.}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.97,0:25:55.28,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aké hlúúúúpe!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.42,0:25:56.18,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zdá sa, že nadišiel čas, aby som ti to ukázala!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.26,0:25:56.77,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ak to nezvládneš, necháme ťa tam!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.85,0:25:56.77,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Všetci vyzeráte byť zaneprázdnení.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.77,0:25:58.05,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prosím, buď v poriadku!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.05,0:25:59.03,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kanade!
